  <description><![CDATA[<div>
<p><span>A highly recommended combination encompassing the best scenery the Fjord Norway region has to offer – starting in the fjordside village of </span><a data-udi="umb://document/a09d8dda0d4f48d68be229cdaeb2f377" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/norway/balestrand" title="Balestrand">Balestrand</a><span> on the mighty Sognefjord, you will have an opportunity to travel on the famous Flåm railway or visit Fjaerland with its Glacier Museum. From here, your included transfer will take you over the magical Gauler Mountains to </span><a data-udi="umb://document/14f6ab787ad2493ab23ce60aa9f14e6a" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/norway/loen" title="Loen">Loen</a><span> on the Nordfjord with its spectacular glacier and sparkling lakes. The areas that surround Loen are arguably home to the fjords’ greatest display of natural beauty and there are good walking opportunities here especially now with the addition of the new Skylift cable-car. The last leg of your journey takes you to the Atlantic Coast and the Art Nouveau city of </span><a data-udi="umb://document/4796d8535a46439d92020f8a158e7c03" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/norway/alesund" title="Alesund">Ålesund</a><span>, where regular boats take visitors to the surrounding small islands and fishing skerries. </span></p>
<p> </p>
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-norway/fjord-explorer#Tour highlights">Tour highlights</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-norway/fjord-explorer#Itinerary">Itinerary</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-norway/fjord-explorer#Your holiday includes">Your holiday includes</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-norway/fjord-explorer#Hotels">Hotels </a>| <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-norway/fjord-explorer#Departure dates">Departure dates</a></h2>
