<h2><a name="Tour highlights"></a><span class="geolocation-title">Tour highlights</span></h2>
<ul>
<li>Beautiful express boat transfer from Bergen to Balestrand</li>
<li>Travel through the Gauler mountains from Balestrand to Loen</li>
<li>Discover both the Nordfjord and Sognefjord</li>
<li>Visit the Aksla viewpoint for panoramic views over <span>Ålesund</span></li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: right;"><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-norway/fjord-explorer#Tour highlights">[Back to top]</a></p>
<h2><a name="Itinerary"></a><span class="geolocation-title">Itinerary</span></h2>
<p><strong>Day 1: UK to Balestrand</strong></p>
<p>Fly to Bergen airport and transfer to<span> </span><a data-udi="umb://document/a09d8dda0d4f48d68be229cdaeb2f377" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/norway/balestrand" title="Balestrand">Balestrand</a><span> </span>on the Sognefjord, known as ‘King of the Fjords’ for being the longest and deepest fjord in Norway and stretching over 200km. Exploring this fjord is a real treat with an opportunity to enjoy picturesque boat trips, gentle walking routes along the shore, the impressive Jøstedal glacier and the world’s steepest gauge railway from Flåm.</p>
<p><strong>Day 4 or 5: Balestrand to Loen</strong></p>
<p>A spectacular 3 hour drive over the magical Gauler mountains to<span> </span><a data-udi="umb://document/14f6ab787ad2493ab23ce60aa9f14e6a" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/norway/loen" title="Loen">Loen</a><span> </span>on the Nordfjord, your base for the next 3 or 4 nights. Trips to the famous Geiranger Fjord or to the emerald lakes and ice-blue glaciers of the Lodal and Briksdal valleys are a must and the new Skylift cable-car from the village provides further exploring opportunities with several walking trails at the top, not to mention the views. The spa and pool facilities at the Hotel Alexandra provide a great setting to relax and unwind after your day out.</p>
<p><strong>Day 8: Loen to Ålesund </strong></p>
<p>Another scenic transfer to the vibrant Art Nouveau city of<span> </span><a data-udi="umb://document/4796d8535a46439d92020f8a158e7c03" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/norway/alesund" title="Alesund">Ålesund</a><span> </span>allows you to sit back and admire the spectacular scenery of the Nordfjord and Sunnmøre regions up close. Once in Ålesund, explore its museums, discover its interesting architecture and surrounding islands or simply take a stroll along its pretty waterfront.</p>
<p><strong>Day 11 or 12: Ålesund to UK </strong></p>
<p>Return by shuttle to Ålesund airport for your flight back to the UK.</p>
<p style="text-align: right;"><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-norway/fjord-explorer#Tour highlights">[Back to top]</a></p>
<h2><a name="Your holiday includes"></a><span class="geolocation-title">Your holiday includes</span></h2>
<ul>
<li>Return flights from the UK</li>
<li>Scenic transfers to and from the airport and between each resort*</li>
<li>Accommodation with private facilities throughout</li>
<li>Half board meals included in Balestrand (Hotel Kviknes only) and Loen</li>
<li>Bed &amp; Breakfast in Ålesund &amp; Balestrand (Hotel Midtnes only)</li>
<li>'Meet &amp; Greet' service throughout your stay, with a welcome to the resort and 24/7 phone service</li>
</ul>
<p>*For guests arriving into Bergen on indirect flights via Amsterdam, transfers from Bergen airport to Balestrand will be by minibus. For all other guests, transfers will be by coastal express boat (transfer from airport to boat quay included)</p>
<p><span></span><strong>Your holiday excludes:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Any extras, drinks, gratuities and personal expenses</li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: right;"><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-norway/fjord-explorer#Tour highlights">[Back to top]</a></p>
<h2><a name="Hotels"></a><span class="geolocation-title">Hotels</span></h2>
<p><strong>Standard Hotels</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><strong>★★+  <a data-udi="umb://document/e6e72ed8f54b4b799df9821bf732b69d" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/norway/balestrand/midtnes-hotel" title="Midtnes Hotel">Hotel Midtnes</a>, Balestrand</strong></li>
<li><strong>★★★+ <a data-udi="umb://document/7780b99803294b0f8a9519ed836b9830" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/norway/loen/loenfjord-hotel" title="Loenfjord Hotel">Hotel Loenfjord</a>, Loen</strong></li>
<li><strong>★★★+  <a data-udi="umb://document/89e354afa6824ae197da03b9604055e7" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/norway/alesund/first-hotel-atlantica" title="First Hotel Atlantica">First Hotel Atlantica</a>, Ålesund</strong></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Superior Hotels </strong></p>
<ul>
<li><strong>★★★★ <a data-udi="umb://document/d26dcba440054402b9ccfe7166c1ad56" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/norway/balestrand/kviknes-hotel" title="Kviknes Hotel">Hotel Kviknes</a>, Balestrand</strong></li>
<li><strong>★★★★+ <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/norway/loen/alexandra-hotel" title="Alexandra Hotel">Hotel Alexandra</a>, Loen</strong></li>
<li><strong>★★★★ <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/norway/alesund/hotel-brosundet" title="Hotel Brosundet">Hotel Brosundet</a>, Ålesund</strong></li>
</ul>
<p><em>Monday departures (11 nights) - 4 nights Balestrand, 3 nights Loen, 4 nights Ålesund</em></p>
<p><em>Friday departures (10 nights) - 3 nights Balestrand, 4 nights Loen, 3 nights Ålesund</em></p>
<h2><a name="Departure dates"></a><span class="geolocation-title">Departure dates<a></a></span></h2>
<ul>
<li>Any Monday or Friday throughout the summer</li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: right;"><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-norway/fjord-explorer#Tour highlights">[Back to top]</a></p>]]></description>
